      • QueryPersonTimeIntervalType

        public QueryPersonTimeIntervalType(String cpr,
                           long beginTimeInterval,
                           long endTimeInterval,
                           String codeSystem,
                           String codeListInBarSeparatedFormat)
        Construct a query for a given person in a given time interval and only those observations that match a given set of types of observations.
        Parameters:
        cpr - CPR of person
        beginTimeInterval - start of interval in Unix time milliseconds
        endTimeInterval - end of interval
        codeSystem - HL7 OID of the code system used in the list of codes below.
        codeListInBarSeparatedFormat - the list of codes as one string separated by vertical bar "|". If you have an array of codes, use the Utility converter functions to produce this string.
